DataMigrate.TransferObjects

Class RequirementObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataMigrate.TransferObjects.RequirementObject

  • public class RequirementObject
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will contain all of the data regarding one requirement entry(row) to be inserted into the database. Created by Anthony Orio on 5/2/2017.
